high_descs: Head past the right side of the island to the coffee machine on the counter.
Open the cabinet under the coffee machine and pick up the big bowl in there.
Bring the bowl up to the counter.
Put the bowl on the counter next to the coffee machine.
Pick up the egg on the back of the counter.
Put the egg in the bowl on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put an egg in a bowl on the counter.

high_descs: Turn to your right and go to the windows at the end of the room, then turn left and go to the cabinets straight ahead, below the coffee maker.
Open the cabinets below the coffee maker and remove a bowl.
Step closer to the cabinet in front of you.
Set the bowl on the counter in front of you.
Pick up the egg on the counter that is the furthest to the back.
Place the egg in the bowl on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put an egg in a bowl, on the counter.

high_descs: Turn right, walk forward to the wall, then turn left and walk forward across the room to the coffee machine on the counter.
Open the cabinets below the coffee machine and take out the bowl, then close the cabinets.
Bend up from the cabinets and face the counter top.
Put the bowl on the counter top, in front of the apple.
Pick up the egg in the back from the counter top.
Put the egg in the bowl.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with an egg in it on a counter top.
